Razgulay Drops Third Day as White Sugar Slides in London

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-09-13T15:45:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/razgulay-drops-third-day-as-white-sugar-slides-in-london-trade.html
OAO Razgulay, the Russian sugar
producer, fell for a third day after sugar dropped in  London .  The shares lost 0.8 percent to 35.90 rubles by the 6.45
p.m. close in Moscow, their weakest close since Aug. 26.  White sugar slipped as much as 2.6 percent, or $20, to
$753.70 a ton on the NYSE Liffe exchange in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Serkin at 
 gserkin@bloomberg.net  